metadata.name: Matisse’s Ferrari
metadata.description:
Matisse’s Ferrari or the way to explore basic desires.

From Forgotten Classic series.

Analysis of the Maslow Pyramid. Having satisfied the need for food, sleep, warmth, a human is then puzzled by the sexual issue and social recognition, after which he reaches a level at which one can already engage in self-actualization.

***
On permanent display at the digital part of Louvre, Paris since 2022
8917 x 6762 pixels
